snippet.title: PUBG: NEW STATE | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
IT'S OFFICIAL!

PUBG: NEW STATE, the latest title by KRAFTON, Inc. and PUBG Studio, the creators of the original battle royale, PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS, will become available around the world starting on November 11, 2021.

Pre-register today at https://pubg.info/3ktVnxp to get notified when launch day arrives, so that you and your friends can dive in and conquer the battlegrounds of 2051.

- Official website: https://pubg.info/3lZw9aB
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/OfficialPUBGNEWSTATE
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/PUBG_NEWSTATE
- Instagram: http://instagram.com/pubgnewstate

#pubgnewstate #newstate #pubg
